<span id="freeTextContainer3127752886374640416">Judy Blume keeps the laughter coming with this book. Fudge makes a new friend while Peter struggles with what feels like the loss of a friend. This did seem to be the weakest of the Fudge books. It was however a perfect set up for the last book in the series. <br/></span>

          </span>
