        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2915017241" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14528637102298043420">Oh Fudge, Fudge and family go on a summer vacation in Maine , very close to Sheilas family, much to Peter, Fudges big brother surprise and horror!</span>

          </span>
